 | year = 2005
 | month = 
 | day = 
 | title = Mitochondria and calcium signaling
 | journal = Cell Calcium
 | volume = 38
 | issue = 3-4
 | pages = 311-317
 | pmid = 16087232
 | doi = 10.1016/j.ceca.2005.06.011
 | url = http://linkinghub.elsevier.com/retrieve/pii/S0143416005000965
 | language = en
 | access-date = 2011-09-04
 | archive-date = 2019-12-01
 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20191201113149/https://linkinghub.elsevier.com/retrieve/pii/S0143416005000965
 | dead-url = no
 }}</ref>
* [[线粒体钠-钙交换体|线粒体钠-钙交换体]]（mitochondrial sodium-calcium exchanger，MNCX），可在将[[钠离子|钠离子]]运出线粒体基质的同时将钙离子运入线粒体基质。

